OL,3,CBowel cancer survivor urges others to
OL,4,Ctake the test that saved his life
OL,6,FBowel cancer survivor John Withers is
OL,7,Furging others to take the test that
OL,8,Fsaved his life more than 15 years ago.
OL,10,FApril is bowel cancer awareness month
OL,11,Fand people across the country are
OL,12,Fbeing urged to get screened.
OL,14,FJohn is from Dumfries and Galloway and
OL,15,Fwas diagnosed with the cancer in 2009
OL,16,Fafter he took a routine screening test.
OL,18,FHe had no symptoms at the time of the
OL,19,Ftest and is urging others to also take
OL,20,Fthe test as catching it early is
OL,21,Fcrucial to recovery.
