OL,3,CBowel cancer survivor urges others to
OL,4,Ctake the test that saved his life
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Border John Withers
OL,7,Fsaid: "Losing weight or pain in your
OL,8,Ftummy, those kind of symptoms, I had
OL,9,Fnothing like that.
OL,11,F"If you receive a kit through the post
OL,12,Fto do a bowel screen test to do it and
OL,13,Freturn it.
OL,15,F"It is a very simple test, it is a
OL,16,Ffree test and you don't get much free
OL,17,Fin life but doing this test can
OL,18,Fliterally save your life. I know that
OL,19,Fbecause it saved mine."
