OL,3,CBowel cancer survivor urges others to
OL,4,Ctake the test that saved his life
OL,6,FMr Withers had emergency surgery to
OL,7,Fremove his bowel after his cancer was
OL,8,Fdiscovered. The operation was
OL,9,Fsuccessful and he has been able to
OL,10,Flive a normal life since.
OL,12,FHis wife Sharon though spoke of the
OL,13,Fexperience when they heard the news
OL,14,Fabout John's diagnosis.
OL,16,FShe said: "That moment when you get
OL,17,Fthe diagnosis everything just changes
OL,18,Fimmediately. I suppose you embark on
OL,19,Fan emotional rollercoaster.
