OL,3,CBowel cancer survivor urges others to
OL,4,Ctake the test that saved his life
OL,6,F"There are no certainties anymore in
OL,7,Fwhat we thought of in being
OL,8,Fcertainties, everything is really in
OL,9,Fflux. It was a difficult time."
OL,11,FMr Withers is urging people to get
OL,12,Ftested even if they are showing no
OL,13,Fsymptoms and is extremely appreciative
OL,14,Fof the support he has received from
OL,15,Fhis wife over the years.
