OL,3,CBowel cancer survivor urges others to
OL,4,Ctake the test that saved his life
OL,6,FHe said: "I wouldn't have seen my
OL,7,Fgrandchildren growing up. They're now
OL,8,F13 and 16 and I have been able to see
OL,9,Ftheir development. Sharon is very
OL,10,Fmodest but Sharon is a huge support to
OL,11,Fme."
OL,13,FAnyone with symptoms of bowel cancer
OL,14,Fis urged to contact their GP and not
OL,15,Fwait for a test.
