OL,3,CBowel cancer survivor urges others to
OL,4,Ctake the test that saved his life
OL,6,FSigns can include stomach pain lasting
OL,7,Fthree weeks or more, blood in stools,
OL,8,Fdiarrhoea or constipation for no
OL,9,Fobvious reason lasting three weeks or
OL,10,Fmore, a feeling of not having emptied
OL,11,Fthe bowels after going to the toilet,
OL,12,Fbottom pain and loose, pale or greasy
OL,13,Fstools.
OL,15,FIf you need any help or advice on this
OL,16,Fsubject, you can get in touch with the
OL,17,Fservices below:
OL,19,FCancer Research UK - Call their cancer
OL,20,Fnurses on 0808 800 4040, open Monday
OL,21,Fto Friday 9am - 5pm
